main event: A civilian woman observed two bright objects in the sky that moved rapidly and disappeared into the clouds.
interesting points: The objects were similar to stars but much brighter., The observation was conducted during daylight under good visibility conditions., The observer reported the objects moving rapidly from one location to another., The objects were visible for approximately 5 minutes before disappearing into the clouds., The reliability of the observer was deemed fair, as she had no technical or scientific background.
sighted object: two bright objects in the sky
